enterprise mobility across iphone operating system ios android and blackberry devices as well as windows and mac os x the company offers good secure emm suites a set of mobile security management productivity and collaboration offerings including application security and containerization identity and access management iam and efss with file level data protection the good secure emm suites integrate the bes and good dynamics platforms and provide enhancements including multiplatform support an architecture for onpremise and cloud deployments and backwards compatibility allowing unification of prior versions of bes its bes cloud is an emm cloud solution for enterprises and small to medium sized businesses bes cloud allows organizations to manage enterprise mobility across ios android windows phone and blackberry  devices as well as samsung knox and android for work devicesthe company offers efss solution with digital rights management drm the company also offers a watchdox application for blackberry  devices providing secure anytime online access to content and supports devices with samsung knox android for work and secure work space for ios and android watchdox technology allows security to travel with shared files on both mobile and desktop devices its secusuite for enterprise is a multios voice encryption software solution that protects mobile calls with a security esbl allows mobile operators to provide customers with monthly bill to subscribe to blackberry emm services and bes worklife by blackberry solution provides a virtual sim allowing the only true carrier grade split billing solution for mobile devicesdevicesthe company focuses its business on enterprise solutions and services the company offers the priv an androidbased device with security and privacy features and support of the android application ecosystem the company also offers and supports devices using the blackberry  operating system it also offers blackberry leap and blackberry porsche design p graphiteblackberry technology solutionsthe blackberry technology solutions business unit consists of five units qnx certicom paratek the blackberry iot platform and intellectual property and patent licensing ippl qnx is a provider of operating systems development tools and middleware for the automotive medical industrial consumer networking and defense markets qnx is engaged in providing software for automotive electronics with products deployed in digital instrument clusters and in the infotainment and telematics systems of over  million vehicles across the world certicom specializes in applied cryptography and key management offering both software components and endtoend security solutions targeted at bandwidth and resourceconstrained applications paratek designs develops and licenses its adaptive radio frequency rf antenna tuning technology the blackberry iot platform connects data generators with data consumers through a platform and application service modules the ippl unit manages the companys portfolio which includes both standardsessential patents and implementation patentsmessagingthe company offers athoc software platform which enables people devices and organizations to exchange information in real time during business continuity and life safety operations the platform securely connects with a set of endpoints including mobile devices running ios and android personal computer pc and mac desktops digital displays radios sirens fire panels and speakers to facilitate collaboration and enhance situational awareness with blackberry messenger bbm the company offers a messaging experience with features such as free voice calling over wireless fidelity wifi oneclick sharing of files and photos dropbox integration location sharing and bbm channels bbm is available on ios android and windows phone platforms android wear and apple watch for enterprise customers the company offers bbm protected for secure enterprise communicationsthe company competes with apple inc samsung vmware inc microsoft corporation mobileiron inc citrix systems inc soti inc sap se ibm corporation htc corporation lg electronics huawei technologies lenovo zte corporation xiaomi inc facebook google line corporation tencent viber kik kakaotalk telegram snapchat ge cumulocity jasper green hills software intel corporation montavista software mentor graphics corporation and sysgo ag » full overview of bbto company address blackberry ltd  university ave ewaterloo   on   nk a p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation john chen  steven capelli  sandeep chennakeshu  carl wiese  marty beard  » more officers  directors blackberry ltd news blackberry wins right to sell secure messaging tools to us government jul   blackberry seeks sales force to match software focus jun   blackberry seeks sales force to match software focus jun   blackberry seeks sales force to match software focus jun   blackberry misses sales forecasts shares tumble jun   » more bbto news related topics stocksstock screenertelecommunications serviceswireless telecommunications services blackberry ltd bbry z wins consumer product gold award  opptrends  news reviews and rumors  home » technology » blackberry ltd bbry z wins consumer product gold award blackberry ltd bbry z wins consumer product gold award moe dresi august  tt technology no comments sharessharetweet blackberry ltd nasdaqbbry today announced that its blackberry z smartphone was named a gold winner in the consumer product of the year category in the best in biz awards  international best in biz awards is the the only independent business awards program judged by members of the press and industry analysts blackberry ltd nasdaqbbry said that its z smartphone is built on its latest blackberry operating system and has full features it said “blackberry z has the largest battery ever built into a blackberry smartphone lasting up to  hours of mixed use” “the blackberry z is an outstanding device for users who demand to stay hyper connected productive and always in control” said ron louks president of devices and emerging solutions blackberry “being honored with a gold best in biz award is a testament to our strategy to develop and deliver innovative technologies that empower professionals” blackberry’s other smartphone z has seen impressive sales in indonesia and india the retailers of blackberry in india are delighted with the sales of the new z device and have reported that it did not take more than two weeks for their stocks to be sold to public since its launch according to a report from economic times blackberry ltd nasdaqbbry tsebb z device has been launched in limited quantities initially and has proven to be a huge success blackberry may soon try its luck in singapore with z blackberry is trying to win back market share lost to rivals apple and samsung with its renowned security features that are unparallelled in the industry according to some analysts since its ceo john chen took over and trying to steer the company back to its roots while trying to win smartphone market share blackberry is also expected to launch two new smartphones the “passport” and the blackberry “classic” image credit crackberrycom blackberry ltd bbry z wins consumer product gold award was last modified may st  by moe dresi sharessharetweet tagsaward best biz blackberry john chen z home » technology » blackberry ltd bbry z wins consumer product gold award about the author moe mo dresi is a computer science student however he has passion for finance and tracking of stock news he has plans of doing his masters degree in finance recent posts can prescott take his game to the next level july   zootopia  – news  updates july   ezekiel elliott’s possible suspension hurting his fantasy value july   thar be giants ‘attack on titan’ season  news july   tapper “no de beats my speed at lbs” july   archives july  june  may  april  march  february  january  december  november  october  september  august  technol